nz.co.jedsimson.lgp.core.environment.operations

Class DefaultOperationLoader<T>

  • nz.co.jedsimson.lgp.core.environment.operations.DefaultOperationLoader<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - Type of the operations to be loaded.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    ComponentLoader<TComponent>, Module, OperationLoader<T>

    public class DefaultOperationLoader<T>
implements OperationLoader<T>

    A simple operation loader implementation that simply loads a set of operations specified by the name of the package + class it can be found in.
